{"tid":1966330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實泛民路線錯曬點解唔屌得？","createTime":"2020-04-10T06:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T18:00:38.000Z","uid":197090,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ef51840ac1a3bedc27570f9d0f82ac8ec9961d97","tid":1966330,"uid":197090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"發現香港好多人都係忽然黃絲 <br />\n泛民俾人叫建制B隊好多年喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪一屌泛民就係熱狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用城寨英雄啲精神勝利法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22abce9d234ba9be6e20fff3e6e921fcc464720d","tid":1966330,"uid":1079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"李斯"},{"pid":"d18bc2864ecc7770cfa37f599335892623845977","tid":1966330,"uid":124722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"Silly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9478d8859cd9175f1347fdebe3948347d4df3e3","tid":1966330,"uid":263086,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJebjw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJebjw3.jpg&h=a0ee34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Laz5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Laz5t.jpg&h=b15df2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為屌得啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做過李斯嘅TVB藝員就係得陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!陳國邦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"46c60a026e53d07545854a480a6b4e25da4d3c9b","tid":1966330,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac292648f0bd49d657649e8c3bb39c97b77b0f0","tid":1966330,"uid":13395,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：唔見你屌下建制藍絲黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0634d68de1ab58f72421bf8edb8c71b84ce36ce5","tid":1966330,"uid":165234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"屌泛民就叻 屌對家唔見屌得咁落力"},{"pid":"e6a14e11618776f91d00800f45960cb8019faa88","tid":1966330,"uid":236414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1ac292648f0bd49d657649e8c3bb39c97b77b0f0","tid":1966330,"uid":13395,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：唔見你屌下建制藍絲黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"兒登仔第日被帽<br />\n條女：唔見你鬧入境淫娃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920ae63aeb5b807da2cbc76a20ac0b9de3918153","tid":1966330,"uid":197090,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c60a026e53d07545854a480a6b4e25da4d3c9b","tid":1966330,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"repl